  "subject": "[PORTALNG] Improve bff release job",
  "commit_message": "[PORTALNG] Improve bff release job\n\n- the existing workflow publishes the bff jar via a\n  shell script that does a PUT on nexus\n- while this principally works, it publishes the artifact\n  with non-standard coordinates and with missing metadata\n- consumers that want to use the library must do so via a\n  rather custom import declaration\n- to fix this, the bff repo was adjusted to use the gradle\n  publish plugin and this change calls this plugin in the ci\n\nIssue-ID: PORTALNG-172\nChange-Id: I4c3738096755258bf06f98eb60a8b55ac08dabf3\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <fiete.ostkamp@telekom.de>\n",
